high_descs: Turn left, walk to the sink and turn right, walk to the left side of the tub.
Pick up the bottle from the upper left corner of the tub.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left side and look down at the cabinet.
Open the cabinet door on the left, put the bottle down to the left of the bar of soap, and close the door.
Move closer to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the bottle from the counter.
Move further away from the counter and look at the cabinet below the sink.
Open the cabinet door, put the bottle in the cabinet to the right of the first bottle, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: To move two bottles to the cabinet.

high_descs: Go across the room to the tub.
Pick up the lotion bottle on the edge of the tub.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Put the lotion bottle in the left cabinet under the sink.
Turn and go to the left side of the sink.
Pick up the lotion bottle on the left side of the sink.
Go back to the left cabinet under the sink.
Put the lotion bottle in the left cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two lotion bottles in the left cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward to face the head of the bath tub.
Pick up the candle on the bath tub.
Turn left to face the left cabinet under the sink.
Place the candle in the left cabinet under the sink.
Turn right to face the front of the bath tub.
Pick up the candle on the bath tub.
Turn left to face the left cabinet under the sink.
Place the candle in the left cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: To move two candles from the bath tub to the left cabinet under the sink.
